00:01:45.649 --> 00:01:54.719
like this…now this piece right here being
it’s right at top I’m not going to thin

00:01:54.719 --> 00:01:59.909
up in here so she doesn’t get a bunch of
little pieces sticking up. I’m then going

00:01:59.909 --> 00:02:52.230
to move over into this top area and very lightly
I’m going to razor up in through here…and

00:02:52.230 --> 00:02:56.830
that is how you go about texturizing the top
part of the hair with a razor which there’s

00:02:56.830 --> 00:02:59.260
